1. "Kad *prestaneš* da se boriš, počinješ da živiš." (When you *stop* fighting, you start living.)

2. "Svi *prestaše* da se smeju kada su video njegovu reakciju." (Everyone *stopped* laughing when they saw his reaction.)

3. "Kad *prestaneš* da misliš o problemima, biće ti lakše da se fokusiraš na dobre stvari." (When you *stop* thinking about problems, it will be easier for you to focus on the good things.)

4. "Kada mu *prestaneš* da veruješ, biće ti puno lakše da se oslobodiš njega." (When you *stop* believing him, it will be much easier for you to free yourself from him.)

5. "Ona *presta* da plače kad je ugledala njegovu izraz lica." (She *stopped* crying when she saw his expression.)